er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;"> Bank of America Corp. offering</a> of 1/1,00=
0ths of its preferred stock, and here is a 2021 <a href=3D"https://link.mai=
l.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30425143.266450/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9Bc=
