<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I used to be a mergers-and-acquisitions lawyer=
, and last year we had some occasion, around here, to <a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30425143.266450/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21=
iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDUtMTMvZWxvbi1tdXNrLXRyb2xscy10d2=
