ortant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bott=
om-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> discuss</a> the <a href=3D"https=
://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30425143.266450/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYm=
xvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDYtMDYvZWxvbi1oYXMtYS1uZXctY=
