e !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; borde=
r-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> mechanics</a> of <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30425143.266450/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDctMDkvZWxvbi1zLW91=
