t; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-st=
yle: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> public-company</a> merger <a href=3D"=
https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30425143.266450/aHR0cHM6Ly93d=
3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDgtMjkvbXVzay10cmllcy1h=
